  "remarks": "\nWISSOL COMMODITIES FZCO is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 based on the following ground: WISSOL COMMODITIES FZCO is and has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian energy sector.  \n",
